"                            codau mynediad a’r manylion yma."

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/check-access-codes.html.twig:43
msgid "Give an organisation access"
msgstr "Rhoi mynediad i sefydliad"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/check-access-codes.html.twig:64
msgid "Active codes"
msgstr "Codau i’w ddefnyddio"

# change to Welsh url
#: src/Actor/templates/actor/check-access-codes.html.twig:66
msgid ""
"Give an organisation their access code so they can view this LPA. They "
"should go to www.gov.uk/view-lpa to use the code."
msgstr ""
"Rhoi cod mynediad i sefydliad i gael gweld yr LPA hon. Dylid mynd i www.gov."
"uk/view-lpa i ddefnyddio’r cod hwn."

