"Rydym wedi anfon dolen i %email% - cliciwch ar y ddolen yn y neges e-bost i "
"gadarnhau’r newid."

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/request-email-change-success.html.twig:25
msgid ""
"The email should arrive in a few minutes, check your spam, bulk and junk "
"folders."
