#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:3
msgid "LPA summary"
msgstr "Crynodeb o’r LPA"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:12
msgid "Back to your <abbr title=\"lasting power of attorney\">LPAs</abbr>"
msgstr "Yn ôl i’ch <abbr title=“atwrneiaethau arhosol“>LPAs</abbr>"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:32
msgid "<abbr title=\"lasting power of attorney\">LPA</abbr> summary"
msgstr "Gweld crynodeb o’r <abbr title=“atwrneiaeth arhosol”>LPA</abbr>"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:40
msgid ""
"This <abbr title=\"lasting power of attorney\">LPA</abbr> has been cancelled"
msgstr "Mae’r <abbr title=“atwrneiaeth arhosol”>LPA</abbr> hon wedi ei chanslo"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:49
msgid ""
"This <abbr title=\"lasting power of attorney\">LPA</abbr> is %status% and "
"can be used now"
msgstr ""
"Mae’r <abbr title=“atwrneiaeth arhosol”>LPA</abbr> hon wedi ei %status% a "
"gallwch nawr ei defnyddio"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:51
msgid "This <abbr title=\"lasting power of attorney\">LPA</abbr> is %status%"
msgstr ""
"Mae’r <abbr title=“atwrneiaeth arhosol”>LPA</abbr> hon wedi ei %status%"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:58
msgid ""
"While you have mental capacity, your attorneys must get your permission to "
"use this <abbr title=\"lasting power of attorney\">LPA</abbr>."
msgstr ""
"Tra bod gennych allu meddyliol, rhaid i’ch atwrneiod gael eich caniatâd chi "
"i ddefnyddio’r <abbr title=“atwrneiaeth arhosol”>LPA</abbr> hon."

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:60
msgid ""
"While the donor has mental capacity, you must get their permission to use "
"this <abbr title=\"lasting power of attorney\">LPA</abbr>."
msgstr ""
"Tra bod gan y rhoddwr allu meddyliol, rhaid i chi gael eu caniatâd i "
"ddefnyddio’r <abbr title=“atwrneiaeth arhosol”>LPA</abbr> hon."

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:63
msgid ""
"This <abbr title=\"lasting power of attorney\">LPA</abbr> can only be used "
"when the donor has lost capacity."
msgstr ""
"Ni ellir defnyddio’r <abbr title=“atwrneiaethau arhosol”>LPA</abbr> hon ond "
"pan nad oes gan y rhoddwr alluedd meddyliol."

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:196
msgid ""
"This <abbr title=\"lasting power of attorney\">LPA</abbr> can be used as "
"soon as it's registered unless instructions say otherwise."
msgstr ""
"Gellir defnyddio’r <abbr title=“atwrneiaethau arhosol”>LPA</abbr> hon cyn "
"gynted ag y bydd wedi’i chofrestru oni bai bod y cyfarwyddiadau yn dweud fel "
"arall."

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:205
msgid ""
"The attorneys have the authority to make decisions about life-sustaining "
"treatment"
msgstr ""
"Mae gan yr atwrneiod awdurdod i wneud penderfyniadau ynglŷn â thriniaeth "
"cynnal bywyd"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:71
msgid ""
"The attorneys do NOT have the authority to make decisions about life-"
"sustaining treatment"
msgstr ""
"NID oes gan yr atwrneiod yr awdurdod i wneud penderfyniadau ynglŷn â "
"thriniaeth cynnal bywyd"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:81
msgid "The donor"
msgstr "Y rhoddwr"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:131
msgid "Name"
msgstr "Enw"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:135
msgid "Date of birth"
msgstr "Dyddiad geni"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:139
msgid "Address"
msgstr "Cyfeiriad"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:98
msgid "Need to change the donor's details?"
msgstr "A oes angen newid manylion y rhoddwr?"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:107
msgid "The attorneys"
msgstr "Yr atwrneiod"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:110
msgid "How decisions are made"
msgstr "Sut y gwneir penderfyniadau"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:113
msgid "Decisions are made by one attorney"
msgstr "Gwneir penderfyniadau gan un atwrnai"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:115
msgid "Attorneys must make decisions jointly (together)"
msgstr "Rhaid i atwrneiod wneud penderfyniadau ar y cyd (gyda’i gilydd)"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:117
msgid ""
"Attorneys can make decisions jointly (together) and severally (separately)"
msgstr ""
"Gall atwrneiod wneud penderfyniadau ar y cyd (gyda’i gilydd) neu yn "
"annibynnol ar ei gilydd (ar wahân)"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:119
msgid ""
"Attorneys must make some decisions jointly (together) and can make some "
"decisions severally (separately). Check the paper <abbr title=\"lasting "
"power of attorney\">LPA</abbr> to find out what decisions must be made "
"jointly."
msgstr ""
"Rhaid i atwrneiod wneud rhai penderfyniadau ar y cyd (gyda’i gilydd) ac "
"maent yn gallu gwneud rhai penderfyniadau yn annibynnol ar ei gilydd (ar "
"wahân) Gwiriwch yr <abbr title=“atwrneiaeth arhosol”>LPA</abbr> papur i gael "
"gwybod pa benderfyniadau y mae’n rhaid eu gwneud ar y cyd."

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:146
msgid "Need to change an attorney's details?"
msgstr "A oes angen newid manylion atwrnai?"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:158
msgid "<abbr title=\"lasting power of attorney\">LPA</abbr> details"
msgstr "Manylion <abbr title=“atwrneiaeth arhosol”>LPA</abbr>"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:162
msgid "Preferences"
msgstr "Dymuniadau"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:165
msgid ""
"Yes, the donor made preferences on their <abbr title=\"lasting power of "
"attorney\">LPA</abbr>.<br>To view these, ask to see the paper <abbr title="
"\"lasting power of attorney\">LPA</abbr>"
msgstr ""
"Do, mae’r rhoddwr wedi nodi dymuniadau yn ei <abbr title=“atwrneiaeth "
"arhosol”>LPA</abbr>. I weld y rhain, gofynnwch am gael gweld y <abbr "
"title=“atwrneiaeth arhosol”>LPA</abbr> papur"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:178
msgid "No"
msgstr "Naddo"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:173
msgid "Instructions"
msgstr "Cyfarwyddiadau"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:176
msgid ""
"Yes, the donor set instructions on their <abbr title=\"lasting power of "
"attorney\">LPA</abbr>.<br>To view these, ask to see the paper <abbr title="
"\"lasting power of attorney\">LPA</abbr>"
msgstr ""
"Do, mae’r rhoddwr wedi rhoi cyfarwyddiadau yn ei <abbr title=“atwrneiaeth "
"arhosol”>LPA</abbr>. I weld y rhain, gofynnwch am gael gweld y <abbr "
"title=“atwrneiaeth arhosol”>LPA</abbr> papur"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:185
msgid ""
"When can the <abbr title=\"lasting power of attorney\">LPA</abbr> be used?"
msgstr ""
"Pa bryd y gellir defnyddio’r <abbr title=“atwrneiaeth arhosol”>LPA</abbr>?"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:189
msgid ""
"You have said that this <abbr title=\"lasting power of attorney\">LPA</abbr> "
"can be used now. While you have mental capacity, your attorneys can only use "
"the <abbr title=\"lasting power of attorney\">LPA</abbr> if you allow them "
"to."
msgstr ""
"Rydych wedi dweud y gellir defnyddio’r <abbr title=“atwrneiaeth "
"arhosol”>LPA</abbr> hon nawr. Tra bod gennych allu meddyliol, rhaid i’ch "
"atwrneiod gael eich caniatâd chi i ddefnyddio’r <abbr title=“atwrneiaeth "
"arhosol”>LPA</abbr>."

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:191
msgid ""
"The donor has said that this <abbr title=\"lasting power of attorney\">LPA</"
"abbr> can be used now. While the donor has mental capacity, you can only use "
"the <abbr title=\"lasting power of attorney\">LPA</abbr> if the donor allows "
"you to."
msgstr ""
"Mae’r rhoddwr wedi dweud y gellir defnyddio’r <abbr title=“atwrneiaeth "
"arhosol”>LPA</abbr> hon nawr. Tra bod gan y rhoddwr allu meddyliol, rhaid i "
"chi gael caniatâd y rhoddwr i ddefnyddio’r <abbr title=“atwrneiaeth "
"arhosol”>LPA</abbr>."

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:194
msgid ""
"This <abbr title=\"lasting power of attorney\">LPA</abbr> can only be used "
"when the donor has lost capacity"
msgstr ""
"Ni ellir defnyddio’r <abbr title=“atwrneiaethau arhosol”>LPA</abbr> hon ond "
"pan nad oes gan y rhoddwr alluedd meddyliol"

# Should be:
