#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:202
msgid "Life sustaining <br>treatment"
msgstr "Triniaeth <br>cynnal bywyd"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:207
msgid ""
"The attorneys do not have the authority to make decisions about life-"
"sustaining treatment"
msgstr ""
"Nid oes gan yr atwrneiod yr awdurdod i wneud penderfyniadau ynglŷn â "
"thriniaeth cynnal bywyd"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:209
msgid ""
"To view this, ask to see the paper <abbr title=\"lasting power of attorney"
"\">LPA</abbr>"
msgstr ""
"I weld y manylion hyn, gofynnwch am gael gweld y <abbr title=“atwrneiaethau "
"arhosol”>LPA</abbr> papur"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:216
msgid "Date donor signed <abbr title=\"lasting power of attorney\">LPA</abbr>"
msgstr ""
"Y Dyddiad y llofnododd y rhoddwr yr <abbr title=“atwrneiaethau "
"arhosol“>LPAs</abbr>"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:221
msgid "Registration date"
msgstr "Dyddiad cofrestru"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:226
msgid "<abbr title=\"lasting power of attorney\">LPA</abbr> reference number"
msgstr "Cyfeirnod <abbr title=“atwrneiaethau arhosol”>LPA</abbr>"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:241
#: src/Actor/templates/actor/check-lpa.html.twig:60
msgid "Warning"
msgstr "Rhybudd"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/view-lpa-summary.html.twig:242
msgid ""
"You cannot use a download or print out of this <abbr title=\"lasting power "
"of attorney\">LPA</abbr> summary in place of the original paper <abbr title="
"\"lasting power of attorney\">LPA</abbr> or instead of giving someone an "
"access code."
msgstr ""
"Ni ellir defnyddio’r crynodeb hwn o’r <abbr title=“atwrneiaethau "
"arhosol”>LPA</abbr> yn lle’r <abbr title=“atwrneiaethau arhosol”>LPA</abbr> "
"papur gwreiddiol neu yn lle rhoi cod mynediad i rywun."

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/instructions-preferences.html.twig:16
msgid "Instructions and preferences"
msgstr "Cyfarwyddiadau a dymuniadau"

#: src/Actor/templates/actor/instructions-preferences.html.twig:21
msgid ""
"If an <abbr title=\"lasting power of attorney\">LPA</abbr> has instructions "
"or preferences we cannot show these online. Organisations might ask to see "
"the paper <abbr title=\"lasting power of attorney\">LPA</abbr> so that they "
"can read the instructions and preferences."
msgstr ""
